collection_holder_name: Arts Library, Special Collections, University of California at Los Angeles (UCLA)
pageContext.collection_title: Eugene Rodney Collection of Scripts and Production Material
pageContext.collection_description: Consists of radio, television and motion picture scripts and production material. Includes radio scripts for Father Knows Best, 1950-1954. Also includes correspondence and stills, some of which are related to the Robert Young-Eugene Rodney Production Co.
